        <Parent_String>fore-and-aft-rigged vessels [300233021], sailing vessels by rig type [300233020], sailing vessels [300233013], watercraft by method of propulsion [300232945], watercraft by specific type [300219289], watercraft [300042940], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
